## Rules
- Always follow the SRS in docs/SRS.md as the source of truth.
- Use clean architecture:
  - db or lib/db for Prisma client
  - lib/services for business logic
  - lib/validators for Zod schemas
  - app/api/* for route handlers
  - app/(routes)/* for pages
- Implement soft delete using deletedAt timestamps.
- Enforce team membership on all team/project/issue routes.
- Use Zod for validation.
- Cache AI responses per SRS rules (summary, suggestion, comment summary).
- Keep code clean, modular, and typed.

## Before coding
Always propose:
1. Schema changes (Prisma)
2. API structure (input/output)
3. UI entry points

Use English for all code unless I request otherwise.
